import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material';

const Component1 = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg">
      {/* Header */}
      <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', my: 3 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" sx={{ color: '#2196f3' }}>
          To-Do App!
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      {/* Calendar header */}
      <Box sx={{ 
        display: 'flex', 
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        gap: 4,
        mb: 3
      }}>
        {['Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat', 'Sun'].map((day) => (
          <Typography key={day} variant="subtitle1">
            {day}
          </Typography>
        ))}
      </Box>

      {/* Search bar */}
      <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <input
          type="text"
          placeholder="Search..."
          style={{
            width: '100%',
            padding: '12px',
            borderRadius: '20px',
            border: '1px solid #ddd',
            fontSize: '16px'
          }}
        />
      </Box>

      {/* Grid layout for boxes */}
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Học Tập */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Học Tập
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Công Việc */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Công Việc
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Gia Đình */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Gia Đình
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Hàng Ngày */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Hàng Ngày
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Hàng Tháng */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Hàng Tháng
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Hàng Năm */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Box sx={{
            bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
            borderRadius: 2,
            p: 3,
            height: 150,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            cursor: 'pointer',
            '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#eeeeee' }
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Hàng Năm
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Component1;
